On 4/29/2010 1:23 PM, Avocado Tom Tarka wrote:
> Are you saying 1000 lbs from a "not overheating" perspective
> or a "frame" perspective?
>

For a 1971, max towing weight is 1100 lbs.  This is per VW.

Later buses are 1322 lbs (manual says you can go higher if the trailer 
has brakes).  110 lbs is the max tongue weight.

 From a "not overheating" perspective, well that's very much a YMMV 
thing... :)

